{"tid":2378924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古] 有無人記得許美靜?","createTime":"2021-01-25T01:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T02:00:57.000Z","uid":304179,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97981b72739740a53b0fb8472eabcdea85417aa3","tid":2378924,"uid":304179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"許美靜（英語：Mavis Hee；1974年9月27日－），原名許美鳳，新加坡女歌手，在1990年代後期於台灣、中國大陸、新加坡等國語流行音樂市場上受歡迎。曾與許茹芸和李翊君被譽為「上華唱片三天后」。2000年後隱出流行音樂界，開始從事公益活動。2006年6月曾出現於媒體，之後因精神狀況欠佳而淡出。<br />\n<br />\n1997年以粵語歌曲《明知故犯》和《傾城》兩首廣東歌曲打進香港與東南亞市場，兩首歌收入於精選集《靜聽精彩13首》，當時在香港佔據流行榜冠軍達3周，在香港銷售超過20萬，已是當時香港天王天后級別的成績，新加坡也超過10萬。她曾被稱為「小王菲」與「天后殺手」，更憑《明知故犯》勇奪香港電台十大中文金曲頒獎禮的「十大中文金曲獎」。<br />\n<br />\n原本好紅，後尾痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383809684cf368678b5851525cb7123c9237d6e4","tid":2378924,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"勁野，<br />\n好鍾意聽"},{"pid":"3ff3e8aa514efa2b3894de6a14a1226885890638","tid":2378924,"uid":304179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383809684cf368678b5851525cb7123c9237d6e4","tid":2378924,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"勁野，<br />\n好鍾意聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6ZSsSl9SWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG6ZSsSl9SWw&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=163e8d66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6ZSsSl9SWw</a><br />\n<br />\n唱得好好聽<br />\n仲要係live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9105d96a5d08b35b25a99a6d28a9941b1a37c","tid":2378924,"uid":381575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:44:39.000Z","msg":"傾城"},{"pid":"4e5add075bafbe6c16374d6d4940753b3d141396","tid":2378924,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"好似係痴咗線<br />\n家陣咩情況？"},{"pid":"3e751c2c93cb3ec8122b84d0464aa884963aa067","tid":2378924,"uid":304179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e5add075bafbe6c16374d6d4940753b3d141396","tid":2378924,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"好似係痴咗線<br />\n家陣咩情況？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.juduo.cc/ent/356152.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.juduo.cc%2Fent%2F356152.html&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=f623a28d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.juduo.cc/ent/356152.html</a><br />\n<br />\n幾個月以前，有去新加坡的粉絲偶然遇上了淪落街頭的許美靜，很難想象，曾經的歌壇天后會以這樣的窘況出現在大家面前。一夜之間許美靜街頭賣唱的新聞傳遍網路每個角落。而事實上，許美靜在街頭並不是賣唱，因為她不是為了錢，她的遭遇其實比賣唱更慘，她是去街頭求救的。<br />\n<br />\n到底是何原因讓她走出這一步的？<br />\n<br />\n根據許美靜街頭展示的求救內容顯示：&ldquo;許美靜家人為了爭奪家產，硬拖著她去精神病院，她和敗壞的許家及經紀人陳佳明斷絕所有關係！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7um9By.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7um9By.jpg&h=2c4346e2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}